About
WHITE Beach welcomes you to the hottest beachfront destination. Featuring two Instagram-worthy pools, a chic outdoor restaurant perfect for sunset cocktail-sipping. This is the place to be and to be seen.

    Family Lunch at WHITE beach - AMAZING profiteroles!
    We couldn't not visit WHITE beach during a family holiday at Atlantis. Although my husband and I would have loved to make use of the beach club, obviously toddlers were not allowed here, but we could have lunch in the restaurant and we were not disappointed. The food was delicious, green juices, bread and oil, kale salad, pasta and the most amazing profiterole stack for dessert! Great music, great atmosphere, attentive staff, spotlessly clean and it was no problem getting a lunchtime reservation. The beach club itself looked fabulous, everything you would hope it would be - glamourous, boujee, a vibe. They even had a bird of prey next to the DJ set.

  • C B
    San Francisco, California2 contributions
    Dubais White Beach Club Nails It!
    Service is top-notch, I was greeted warmly by not just the service representative. But by Security, as well. I already knew what I wanted in terms of a reservation, and there was availability, granted, I did arrive just at opening. The representative walked me over to the pool where I was going to be spending the day with my wife and she explained the amenities and restaurant availability. I was waited on by a very friendly chap, Mr. Aiban, who was very attentive throughout my entire stay, constantly refilling the ice bucket, and taking care of my orders promptly and with diligence. The restaurant was terrific: we had the dragon roll and beef tartare along with a meringue dessert; we very much enjoyed the meal. The changing room and bathroom is roomy, but just enough. There are two showers in the mens side and you can lock the door while you are in the shower and there is a small changing area adjacent to the shower stall. Everything is nice, clean, and tidy. The facility is extremely well-maintained, the view of the water leading to the Persian Gulf is lovely and tranquil. Note: you are looking at two story residences across the way, but you have a metropolitan skyline beyond that which I enjoyed viewing. As you face the water, the sun will set to your right. If it is very windy, umbrellas may not always be opened. Make sure you bring everything you normally would to a beach club as prices are quite high, although the quality is top-notch. White Beach is a terrific beach club, destination, and one more thing, the DJ plays an awesome mix nonstop you just cant help but get into that beach club vibe! Well done, White Beach organization!
    WHITE Beach Management

Nicole
Nottingham, UK9 contributions
Lovely Experience!
Nov 2024 Family
I visited Whites with my family, the beach club is beautiful, lovely pool area and easy beach access. The music was really good! Food was lovely, even if the staff did forget some of the side dishes, which was rectified eventually.

One thing however, we was unaware that you were not able to redeem the food credit you received when booking in the restaurant, so we had to eat on our sun lounger. The restaurant was empty (wonder why) and unsure what the difference is.

The showers/toilets were immaculate and lovely!!

There are also helicopters taking off and landing very frequently, right next to the beach club, but this didnt really bother us.

Getting a taxi out of the beach club was a task and we ended up doing a small hike down the main road to find one.

Apart from this, we cant wait to return to Whites.
Written November 12, 2024
